FBIS3-14152 "drnes056_n_94001" FBIS-NES-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Mar 1994 LEBANON Al-Hariri Contacted by Christopher, al-Shar NC2303123794 Shanayh Voice of the Mountain in Arabic 1000 GMT 23 Mar 94 NC2303123794 Shanayh Voice of the Mountain Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] According to informed sources, Prime Minister al-Hariri was contacted by U.S. Secretary of State Warren Christopher. They discussed the escalating Israeli hostilities and the resistance's legitimate response to these attacks. Christopher also contacted his Syrian counterpart Faruq al-Shar' asking him to make quick contacts to curb the military escalation in south Lebanon.
